{"tid":2199013,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"王毅稱個別國家肆無忌憚監控　拉夫羅夫指美國挑撥離間","createTime":"2020-09-11T23:00:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-12T00:46:10.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"eca6edbae8460a8b80191c35e4c7b4f87cb11609","tid":2199013,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T23:00:36.000Z","msg":"外長王毅在莫斯科與俄羅斯外長拉夫羅夫會談。<br />\n<br />\n《新華社》報道，王毅強調，網絡與信息安全是中俄以及國際合作的重要領域。當前個別國家憑藉自身科技實力，肆無忌憚監控他國，竊取別國信息。中方日前提出「全球數據安全倡議」，目的就是響應各方在數據安全領域的普遍關切和主要疑慮，同各方共同推進數字安全國際規則的制定。<br />\n<br />\n拉夫羅夫表示，當前美國採取破壞性行動，在亞太地區推行充滿冷戰思維的「印太戰略」，在地區國家間挑撥離間，造成分裂甚至對抗。他又表示，俄方積極評價中方提出的「全球數據安全倡議」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1549179-20200912.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1549179-20200912.htm&d=D4HIriwr0d5ovb2eA4y9f9VSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=a2e98fe4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1549179-20200912.htm&h=08b979eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1549179-20200912.htm</a>"},{"pid":"90c4387b5a6769b7df8447a7b72533ea703890b1","tid":2199013,"uid":25525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T23:12:17.000Z","msg":"同美國軍人播毒同一套路"},{"pid":"96372e9452e850a7f6067f99bb67cffd4e755df3","tid":2199013,"uid":91914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T23:17:52.000Z","msg":"中俄又黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ddace28d48c5aac9c28b9dc637f60a92c11d194","tid":2199013,"uid":204533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96372e9452e850a7f6067f99bb67cffd4e755df3","tid":2199013,"uid":91914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T23:17:52.000Z","msg":"中俄又黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T23:30:26.000Z","msg":"俄仔得把口, 發下口痕增加自己身價, 拎多啲著數之麻( 